## Integration Test Matrisi

Zorunlu senaryolar:
- `USER` → `/admin/*` → `403`
- `ADMIN` → list bypass (deaktive owner campaign görünür)
- Son admin role demote → `422` `LAST_ADMIN`
- Deactivate → refresh invalid + audit row
- Content PATCH → `CONTENT_EDITED` audit insert
- Audit tablosunda UPDATE/DELETE API yok

## AdminService vs Domain Service

Admin content PATCH domain validation reuse (`UpdateCampaignDto`) ama **policy bypass** — doğrudan Prisma update. Normal `CampaignsService.update` member'a 403 döner; admin path ayrı method.

```typescript
// admin.service.ts — bypass visibility/membership
async adminUpdateCampaign(actorId: string, id: string, dto: UpdateCampaignDto) {
  // no CampaignPolicy.canUpdate — ADMIN işlemi
  const updated = await this.prisma.campaign.update({ where: { id }, data: dto });
  await this.auditLog.log({ /* CONTENT_EDITED */ });
  return { data: updated };
}
```

## Admin User List Filtreleri

Query: `search`, `role`, `isActive`, cursor pagination. Deaktive kullanıcılar listede görünür (admin tam görünürlük).

## Official Content Admin Edit

Seed official homebrew — admin `PATCH /admin/homebrew/:id` ile düzenleyebilir [AP-001]. Audit `CONTENT_EDITED` zorunlu.

## Audit Action Enum

`packages/shared` ve Prisma enum uyumlu:
- `ROLE_CHANGED`
- `USER_DEACTIVATED` / `USER_REACTIVATED`
- `CONTENT_EDITED` / `CONTENT_DELETED`

Target type: `USER`, `CAMPAIGN`, `CHARACTER`, `HOMEBREW`.

## Transaction: Role Change + Audit

Role change ve audit aynı `$transaction` — partial failure olmamalı.

## Admin DELETE Cascade

Campaign delete → dm_notes, members, characters `campaign_id` set null veya cascade — `docs/02` Bölüm 4. Admin delete audit `CONTENT_DELETED` metadata'da `targetName`, `ownerId`.

## Admin Panel API Prefix

Tüm `/admin/*` — global prefix sonrası `/api/v1/admin/users`. FE admin route ayrı; backend tek prefix.

## Normal User vs Admin Path

Aynı entity için iki path:
- `/campaigns/:id` — policy kısıtlı
- `/admin/campaigns/:id` — ADMIN only, bypass, audit

Admin path kullanıldığında audit — normal path'te kullanıcı kendi kaynağını edit → audit yok.

## Audit Log Okuma (MVP)

Read endpoint yok — DB direct query veya post-MVP UI. `AuditLogService` yalnızca `log()` export.

## Anti-pattern'ler

- ❌ Admin route without `@Roles(Role.ADMIN)`
- ❌ Admin write without audit log
- ❌ `audit_logs` UPDATE/DELETE (Prisma veya raw)
- ❌ Son admin korumasını atlama
- ❌ Deactivate without refresh revoke
- ❌ Admin list'te normal USER visibility filtresi
- ❌ Normal user CRUD için audit log (gürültü)
- ❌ Audit log admin UI placeholder (MVP dışı)
- ❌ `password_hash` veya token audit metadata'da
- ❌ Admin işlemini guard'sız public endpoint
- ❌ Admin service'de `CampaignPolicy` ile self-block
- ❌ İki admin path'i tek controller'da `@Roles` olmadan birleştirme

